title: 10 More Books - October 2015 (gnv64)
description:
A collection of 10 more books for this month, this time all in PDF format:

01. Financial Management for Decision Makers (7th Ed) by Peter Atrill
02. Incredible Space Missions by Gary Jeffrey, Mike Lacey
03. Mathematical Amazements and Surprises by Alfred S. Posamentier and Ingmar Lehmann
04. Parabolas of Science Fiction by Brian Attebery (Editor)
05. People on People - The Oxford Dictionary of Biographical Quotations
06. Psychopathology - History, Diagnosis, and Empirical Foundations (2nd Ed)
07. Reading Statistics and Research (6th Ed) by Schuyler W. Huck
08. Viva in Biochemistry (2nd Ed) by M.N. Chatterjea
09. Worlds Beyond - Our Own The Search for Habitable Planets by Sujan Sengupta
10. Writing for IELTS by Anneli Williams
